      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Candidate A's communication style is professional and empathetic, demonstrating a structured approach to problem-solving and customer service. They show respect for the customer's feelings and provide a thoughtful solution, which is ideal for a client-facing role.\n\nCandidate B's communication style, while attempting to be empathetic, lacks professionalism and clarity. Their use of slang and less formal language may not be suitable for a client-facing position, as it could come across as unprofessional and may not convey the seriousness of the situation effectively.",
